They have free internet in the lobby and a courtesy Fiat 500 for 4 hours during your stay which is great.	The hotel lobby is extremely small and really unsuitable to wind down after a day spent strolling through the magnificent city that is Barcelona.	Apparently they are building a major new fast-train station right outside so you can imagine the amount of work involved.	Though the rooms are nice, the reception and corridors are a bit basic and lacking for a four star hotel.